LongoMatch-0.18.17 "TV"
-----------------------------

The LongoMatch team is happy to announce the seventeenth release in the
stable 0.18 series.

Due to its dependency on GStreamer, We strongly recommend to have
all official latest gstreamer libraries and plugins installed for the best user
experience.

* Features
	* Add menu option to duplicate tags
	* Differentiate tags with colors by team in the timeline
	* Add players stats
	* Use bigger buttons in the fake live analysis
	* Support detaching the player with playlists

* Bugs fixed
	* Resize tagger dialog when it's bigger than the screen
	* Respect config for the edition properties
	* Handle corrupt databases
	* Don't duplicate the 1x speed in the control bar

*Contributors to this Release:

  * LongoMatch:
	Andoni Morales Alastruey <ylatuya@gmail.com>

* Requirements

 * mono >= 2.4
 * mono-posix >= 2.4
 * mono-cairo >= 2.4
 * gstreamer >= 0.10.30
 * gnonlin >= 0.10.15
 * gtk-sharp >= 2.12
 * db40 >= 7.4


* Download
  LongoMatch source tarballs are available on gnome FTP:
   http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/longomatch/0.18/

  See the website for distribution-specific packages.

* Information and Feedback

 * Information for users and developers can be found on the LongoMatch website :
  http://www.longomatch.ylatuya.es/

 * Bugs and Features Requests
  http://bugzilla.gnome.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=longomatch


